race.comment: SAN FRAN (3) was safely held in tougher company last start at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 6 lengths at this track (19.76) beating Orana Valerie in a Grade 5 on January 14. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Looks the one to beat on her best form. RUTLAND SNICKERS (4) was below best last time at this track (20.31) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length seventh. Has already won two times from this draw. Can hit the frame with the right run. MARKING TIME (1) scored (22.98) last time out over 388m at Gosford four-and-a-half months ago. Expected to feature on best form. URBAN BREAM (2) is worth including.
